      "x": 108,
      "y": 842,
      "width": 444,
      "height": 186,
      "text": "shared-host pipe\nJSON lines over named pipe\n\nHostClientRequest\n- Attach\n- SubmitPrompt { text, pane_context }\n- SelectRecommendation { choice }\n\nHostServerMessage\n- Attached / SharedStateSnapshot\n- Event / Error / Pong",
