      "x": 856,
      "y": 952,
      "width": 548,
      "height": 186,
      "text": "turn mechanism\n\nrecord_prompt_submission()\nProgressStatus(\"Preparing context...\")\nProgressStatus(\"Thinking...\")\nAgentMessageChunk => pending_agent_response += chunk\nAgentMessageEnd => parse_recommendation_set()\nthen broadcast snapshot / events to attached clients",
